<subSubSection id="C3056534737DAB38FF5CFCF6D63B920A" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA036BF737DAB38FF5CFCF6D63B920A" blockId="21.[151,1437,791,1050]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<emphasis id="B96BEAAD737DAB38FF5CFCF6D647956F" bold="true" box="[197,346,869,895]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Discussion:</emphasis>
Although 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8E4B4E737DAB38FE79FCF6D43E956F" author="Schwoerbel" box="[480,803,869,895]" pageId="21" pageNumber="33" refString="Schwoerbel, J. (1959) Okologische und tiergeographische Untersuchungen uber die Milben (Acari, Hydrachnellae) der Quellen und Bache des sudlichen Schwarzwaldes und seiner Randgebiete. Archiv fur Hydrobiologie Supplement 24, 385 - 546." type="book chapter" year="1959" yearSuffix="p">
Schwoerbel (
<number id="3DD72498737DAB38FD1DFCF6D5DB956F" box="[644,710,869,895]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1959.0">1959</number>
, p. 
<number id="3DD72498737DAB38FD71FCF6D406956F" box="[744,795,869,895]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="526.0">526</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
put 
<taxonomicName id="4C1F4D3C737DAB38FCC4FCF6D371956F" authority="Bader" authorityName="Bader" box="[861,1132,869,895]" class="Arachnida" family="Sperchonidae" genus="Sperchon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="monstruosus">
<emphasis id="B96BEAAD737DAB38FCC4FCF6D304956E" box="[861,1049,869,894]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">S. monstruosus</emphasis>
Bader
</taxonomicName>
into synonymy under 
<taxonomicName id="4C1F4D3C737DAB38FA1CFCF6D66895B6" authority="Halbert" authorityName="Halbert" class="Arachnida" family="Sperchonidae" genus="Sperchon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hibernicus">
<emphasis id="B96BEAAD737DAB38FA1CFCF6D60E95B5" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">S. hibernicus</emphasis>
Halbert
</taxonomicName>
, a placement recorded by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8E4B4E737DAB38FD31FC1FD4C895B6" author="Viets" box="[680,981,908,934]" pageId="21" pageNumber="34" refString="Viets, K. O. (1987) Die Milben des Sußwassers (Hydrachnellae und Halacaridae [part.], Acari). II: Katalog. Sonderbande des Naturwissenschaftlichen Vereins in Hamburg, 8, 1 - 1012." type="journal article" year="1987" yearSuffix="p">
K. O. Viets (
<number id="3DD72498737DAB38FCA5FC1FD46795B6" box="[828,890,908,934]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1987.0">1987</number>
, p. 
<number id="3DD72498737DAB38FC02FC1FD4D095B6" box="[923,973,908,934]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="699.0">699</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8E4B4E737DAB38FC7BFC19D36A95B6" author="Pesic" box="[994,1143,906,934]" pageId="21" pageNumber="33" refString="Pesic, V. (2006) New records of water mites (Acari: Hydrachnidia) from springs and running waters in Bulgaria. Acta Zoologica Bulgarica, 58, 43 - 55." type="journal article" year="2006">
Pešić (
<number id="3DD72498737DAB38FBB6FC1FD37295B6" box="[1071,1135,908,934]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="2006.0">2006</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, perhaps unaware of this change in species status, recorded 
<taxonomicName id="4C1F4D3C737DAB38FDCDFC21D40B95DB" box="[596,790,946,971]" class="Arachnida" family="Sperchonidae" genus="Sperchon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="monstruosus">
<emphasis id="B96BEAAD737DAB38FDCDFC21D40B95DB" box="[596,790,946,971]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">S. monstruosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="F308762F737DAB38FCFFFC21D4C595DC" box="[870,984,946,972]" name="Bulgaria" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Bulgaria</collectingCountry>
. Interestingly, Schwoerbel (
<emphasis id="B96BEAAD737DAB38FAD9FC21D28F95DB" box="[1344,1426,946,971]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">op. cit</emphasis>
) considered 
<taxonomicName id="4C1F4D3C737DAB38FEBBFC4AD6DC95E2" box="[290,449,985,1010]" class="Arachnida" family="Sperchonidae" genus="Sperchon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hibernicus">
<emphasis id="B96BEAAD737DAB38FEBBFC4AD6DC95E2" box="[290,449,985,1010]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">S. hibernicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to be a ‘Mediterranean species’ but it is now known to have a broader European distribution.
</paragraph>
